      <li>Vehicle intake registration and processing management</li>
      <li>Weighbridge integration and tonnage recording</li>
      <li>Scrap and spare parts inventory management</li>
      <li>Compliance documentation per MoRTH Vehicle Scrappage Policy 2021</li>
      <li>B2B management for Registered Vehicle Scrapping Facilities (RVSF)</li>
      <li>B2C portal for individual vehicle owners</li>
      <li>Role-based access control, audit logs, and reporting</li>
      <li>VAHAN portal integration for real-time vehicle data</li>
